<h2 style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">HOW TO WORK IN THE MUSIC BUSINESS</h2>
<strong>Requires hardwork and determination</strong>
<p>Do not forget to work on your  <mark>production skills</mark>helps one understand his genre of music</p>
<em>This is the basic part of music production</em>
