<p><b>Get yourself out there let the your music be a motivation to others and even you yourself.</b></p>

<h1 style="font-style: inherit;">HOW TO SHINE IN THE MUSIC INDUSTRY</h1>
<p><b>First and is have a team that believe in your dreams <br>That will make you push yourself to next level knowing you have people who believe in your work.</b></p>
<p><b>But there is key things to note but first and foremost always have a plan.</b></p>
<p><b>Listen to musician who joined the game before you take only the positive aspect of the conversation.</b></p>
<p><b>The Music Indusrty sometimes may be shady so you must learn the music business.</b></p>
<p><b>Avoid alot of procastination take you master you graft you will enjoy your fruits at the end.</b></p>
<p><b>Helps you figure out the kind of genre you are good and you to specialise on it.</b></p>

<h1><b>TAKE TIME TO LEARN</b></h1>
<P><b>This comes with a alot of pressure but help one discover him or herself.</b></P>
<p><b>As an Arstist or Musician always have something on your sleeve to avoid presssure for funs or management.</b></p>
<p><b>Be Boss by owning your own ideas and work.</b></p>
<p><b>Also good to think outside let not be about music alone build your own brand from the scratch.</b></p>
<p><b>Make yourself vulnerable in the music business because if music doesnt grow old why should you.</b></p>
<p><b>Be bold in your steps as you chase your dreams its you and only you who is in control</b></p>
<p><b>Hundles will always be there thats part of life thats what should make you stronger at the end of the day <br>
let them make stronger,wiser and courageous to make own self decisions but out of it all discpline is the most important virtue of them all.</b></p>

<h1><b>DISCIPLINE</b></h1>
<p><b>In life one of most virtue i can to attribute is discpline.This one virtue can make a rich man poor and a poor man rich.</b></p>
<p><b>Discipline plays a key role even in the decision you make in your daily life activity.</b></p>
<p><b>Human beings we are programmed to our daily discipline though most people call it timetable. <br>
Whats make you follow that timetable to full effect <mark>Discipline</mark></b></p>
<p><b>Though time itself plays a big virtue but now time spent is made possible by discipline</b></p>
<p><b>Even in  music or music business your discipline determines your growth and moves and steps.</b></p>
<p><b>Being in the industry causes alot of attention to move towards you maintaining that fame hasn't being easy for most people. <br>
Some famous people have ended up broke due lack of control for fame and spending indiscipline</b></p>
<p><b>That why in the begining i talked about a <mark>Good team</mark>people who want to see you rise not those who pray for your downfall daily.</b></p>
<p><b>But always remember this world you came alone you will on your grave alone but live well with people there is a swahili saying that says <mark>Watu ni Mali</mark></b>Treat others how you want to be treated in this journey.</p>


